lines.text: You did hear what the man said...
If I heard him, I might have to kill him.
You're rotten, Tennessee, dirty. And what's more, you like it that way.

[in Duchess' bordello]
I've never been in a place like this before.
Don't you worry. You'll feel right at home.
Honey, I never could wait for anything, you know that. Especially trouble.
